messages.content: Barselius enters the place he bought for the first time. it's fucked up and in need of cleaning... He shouldn't have bought the things he did. Still, He puts on the "we are hiring" sign, and starts setting things up

Soleil was walking around, despite the revolution going on, she felt like she needed *something* new to do, as she barely had any missions lately.
Passing by the place, she saw *"we are hiring"* sign and got curious. She walked in the gym "Hello ?"
"Oh hi! " he turned back to see her "i'm still building this up so"
She looked around the place... Definitly needed some cleaning. She turned her head to sigh as she saw Barselius ***"Oh, it's you"***
"Yeah?"
"Why are you opening a gym for ? Some kind of hidden plasma plan ?" Soleil was still very much suspicious of Barselius, and him opening a gym *in the middle of a r√©volution* just looked weird to her
"n-no? i just.... wanted to open up a gym" he says still cleaning the floor "and if you wanna work here tell me too"
She sighed, not really wanting to press further "Fine, What's up with your arm ?" She leaned against the wall
"The bitch in gray managed to explode it off"
She made a disguested face "Oh, *them*. How come one of your kind attacked you like that ?"
"Same reason there's muns on their side"
"... Alright. Fair" She walked up to him "This place is a total mess, it needs a lot of renovations before officially opening"
"yeah, but i need to make some money"
Soleil took off her jacket "Tell me, why did you want to open a gym ?"
"i'm kind of tired of being not good... so i kind of wanted to help people" he sighs "in the only way i know how"

Soleil fell silent, *that's a very Noble goal actually*
She went to take the nearest broom "Let's get this place presentable as soon as possible"
he followed cleaning, and uncovering the boxing ring "This is my pride and glory"
"Oh, a boxing ring, pretty neat" Soleil kept cleaning, she was going as fast as she could.
he did the same "we will finish this today even!" he shows the machines on the gym

"Don't get your hopes up, there's still some other stuff to be done. Those machines don't look half bad"
After a bit of cleaning, she took a short break
he looks at her "Well. i guess we can do some stuff" he huffs "yeah maybe not it all today but it's opening"
"Uh, you really want to open Quick, don't you ?"
"Yeeeeah" he puts a hand behind his head
"Let's try to make it at *least* presentable today then" She stretched
"yeah!" he said getting a mop from the closet "the ground is suposed to be white" it currently is very dusty

"Alright" She summoned her stand, and punched it a few times.
Then, she took a mop in her hands and after the stand touched her, she started moving fast through the Gym, swiping everything in sight
"holy shit you're fast" he's surprised
After she finally stoped, she smiled and waved "My stand can pretty much convert energy, so it can give me a little boost of speed"
"can i try?"
"You're sure ?" She raised an eyebrow
"i meant. supercharging you, you punched your stand so..."
She shook her head "Seeing how strong you are, you'd destroy my arms. Number one rule with stands is that any damages made to the stand goes to the user" She showed her arm, it was slightly bruised
"Oh, got it"  he says "well let's go back to cleaning then"
She nodded and was sliding on the floor again, cleaning it pretty Quickly
Barselius cleaned the main area. And started cleaning the glass walls on the front
After finishing her part, she joined him and was cleaning the glass walls as well
the gym was presentable "i guess it's open now?"
She sat down and sighed, drinking some water "It's fine looking now, so yes"
"now we wait!, i'll go finish tidying up the dumbells and such" and he goes to the weightlifting area
She waved "Good idea, I'll stay near the entrance"
"Nice! the pricings are, 60 ((what's the unity for munny?)) for the month, and if you pay six months in advance it end up being 10 (whatever the munny unit is) cheaper"
"Got it !" She drank some water and took out her Tesseract to look at stuff
Theres a girl standing outside, thinking about entering
Soleil is too busy with her Tesseract to notice her
Barselius finishes up and pats soleil back "done, and. pay attention. there's someone here"
She turned to him "Oh, right, My bad, I didn't hear anyone entering" She put her Tesseract down
"no on the outside" he points out
Her tail swayed a bit as she entered "This place must be new huh? A gym, neat."
"Yeah!" barselius smiles, but the mask covers it "Welcome to the warrior gym!"
"Hold up-" Soleil squint at the mun entering "She seems familiar"
"uh. i don't remember her?"
She stares at Soleil, a little nervous
"uhm. Hi?" he waves at her
She stares right back at her and sigh loudly "Of course you wouldn't, I met her alone. A little coward of a raccoon"
"Rude." She huffs
Soleil gives a very forced laugh "Are you gonna deny it when I clearly saw you run like a little coward last time ?"
"I didn't deny anything." She hissed "I just said rude."
"You're only getting back what you gave" She quietly glared at her
"woah woah. calm down. If you two want to fight. inside there's the ring" he says looking at the two
"It'd be a *pleasure*"
"ok. but you don't think that. she" he points at her "Would tank you... Anyway."
"If a fight is what she want, I'll give her" She shrugged "Although I doubt she'll accept the offer"
"I came here to see if I could start working out not to fight someone twice me fucking size." She growled
"Good. I Just cleaned the gym, would be a shame if it got dirty again" She growled back, and louder, leaning over her
She stepped back, glaring
"heyheyhey No. stop. no fighting yet. God, Wait until the gym actually opens for fights"
Soleil turned to Barselius "Alright, alright. Sorry i got carried away there..."
Mamizou is clearly intimated by Barselius
"here. Nookie. We are open to anyone. feel free to come, and be a part of it"
"I-Im Mamizou by the way....." She mumbled
Soleil quietly whispered to Barselius "Be careful. She's a trickster, and an annoying one at that"
"My name is barselius" he extends a hand for a handshake
Her ears twitch and she just....looks dejected "Thats all people know me as......" She mumbled before shaking his hand. Hers are so tiny compared to his
*That's all you present yourself as* Soleil stayed quiet, despite hearing what she said
"well. come in! you'll be my first customer!"
"I uh....I don't really know where to start...." Shes nervous
"Show her around, I'll stay at the entrance Just in case"
He walks arround showing the machines "well. this is the main area you would work out in"
She nodded a bit, looking everything over

He doesn't take note of it, seeing as how a buff guy at the gym isn't that uncommon (and since he looks smaller than usual from that distance).

He finishes the wiring. And the arm on the gym sign starts flexing and shining a light blue

barselius turns to welcome the newcomers "Welcome to the warr-" he looks at polaris his face fills with anger *Traitor* Deus and Ancilla say

"Barselius‚Äî"

"You own a gym? Good for you," he congratulates, walking forward, a little confused and nervous.

"...?"

he holds back. not. wanting to go and break his new gim, he extends a hand "welcome!" he ignores who polaris even is. he's treating like just another customer *YOU BETRAYED US. YOU FUCKING BETRAYED US, YOU TOLD MORISE AND THAT BITCH CAME KNOCKING ON HIS DOOR. HE IS FUCKING HOMELESS NOW*
She involuntarily shudders. "Jesus. He's... really mad." She mutters.

*I‚Äî What? What the hell are you talking ab‚Äî*
He pauses. Is that why Barselius' arms..
"...That *fucker,*" he growls to himself quietly.
*How the hell did they find out where he was..?* Fuck, *I should've never even talked to him, now his arms..*
"I'm only vaguely aware of who you are." She says, louder, to Barselius. "So I'll start off on good terms. Hello. I'm Uis." She extends a hand to him.
Mamizou is still here but is even more intimidated now. She just. Decides to leave
"Bye!" She waves cheerily at Mamizou.

he holds her hand and shakes it "welcome to the warrior gym. here you train to be strong" 
**THERES NO OTHER REASON TO WHAT HAPPENED. YOURE LUCKY HE'S WEARING A SHIRT THERES AN IMMENSE HOLE UNDER IT STILL**
She inhales strongly at the contact, wincing slightly as the anger runs through her. "Your emotions are running very strongly. Do you want to go calm down somewhere?"
"i'm fine?" barselius is holding back from exploding. Ancilla and Deus are the ones angry

*I have no idea how Morise found him. I'm fuming at this, too,* he thinks to them, honestly confused.
"Barselius. I'm.. Look, I have no idea how Morise found you. But.. it must've been through me, so I'm sorry," he tries to apologize, brain working through the details of that day.
*How did‚Äî* He suddenly realizes. *..Illuvies..*
"hey. relax tiny." he says hiding his anger through the facade
"That's strange. You're either incredibly good at holding back, or you're really not aware... my radar is going haywire, maybe." She releases the handshake and sits down, musing theories to herself.

"It's Ancilla and Deus," he mumbles to Uis.
"Look, I can't relax. I hurt a lot of people‚Äî and I didn't even *know* I hurt you, too. I'm.."
He's struggling to find the words, he himself is just.. so *pissed off.* At Morise, at Illuvies‚Äî He *refuses* to get quaky at the thought of that bastard right now, he's just *mad.*
"It's who now?" She mutters back. "Oh, now you're mad too. Jeez, you two. Calm down."

"here is a place free from war... Anyone who thinks otherwise. can fight me" he looks at them "the pricings are on the wall. It's 60 munny per month. but if you get the subscription of 6 months it goes for 50 munny per month"

"I'm not mad at him," he says, turning to Uis, ignoring Barselius' casualness. "I'm mad at *Morise.* That *fucker* somehow found Barselius and hurt him after I left‚Äî And I'm sure Illuvies was part of it."

Uis, the kind-of leader of the revolution, raises an eyebrow. "I... see." She tilts her head. "Morise is... not the best person." She says slowly. "Just figuring some things out." She crouches beside him. "For now, we came here to work out. It takes your mind off things. We'll dwell on things later."

"Why is it fair I take my mind off of things while Barselius is *MISSING AN ARM?*" he raises his voice a little, before taking a deep breath and trying to calm down. "I. Just keep hurting people. I'm going for a walk," he mumbles, pushing passed Uis and walking out the door without another word.
"You fucking know what. Polaris. Come here. " he says, ancilla and deus are mumbling "Listen... I don't fucking care about this ok. You're just. over fucking reacting" he sighs
"God *fucking* damnit." She gives Barselius an unreadable look and walks after him. Not runs, walks. She can catch up, she has a much longer side.

he stretched himself and got into the ring
